text: Choi Wooshik (born March 26, 1990) is a South Korean actor. He was born in Seoul. He was raised in Canada. Choi gained international recognition with the blockbuster zombie movie Train to Busan and action-adventure movie Okja. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Seoul
